data.description: Welcome to this charming Single-Family home in Orlando! This cozy home features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, perfect for small families or couples. The yard is spacious and well-maintained, providing ample space for outdoor activities. The home is located in a peaceful neighborhood, Close to the Airport and hospitals. Also located near Valencia College East Campus. Don’t miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful home in Orlando!
